    <h4>What is Helping Hand?</h4>
    <p>Helping Hands is a government organisation which takes the initiatives to help those who are in need of food.</p>
    <p>At Helping Hands ,we're on a mission to combat hunger and make a positive impact in our community by delivering nutritious meals to those in need.Partenering with the government and food places,we donate  meals .It's our way of ensuring no one goes to bed hungry.</p><p>Join us in the flight against hunger and help us create a world where everyone has access to nutritious food</p>
